lead safety personal protective equipment page 1 lead safety personal protective equipment department chemical and general safety program lead safety owner program manager john shepardson authority es&h manual chapter 20 lead safety all personnel must follow these safety practices when using personal protective equipment ppe while working with lead or performing lead related work if you use leather gloves for lead handling do not use them for any other work store leather gloves that have been used with lead in a labeled plastic bag other kinds of gloves may also be used such as latex remove ppe before leaving the work area place disposable coveralls into the proper hazardous waste bags immediately after use see chapter 17 hazardous waste clean and store protective equipment including your respirator according to proper procedures see chapter 29 respirator program for information on cleaning respirators 20 november 2005 slac i 730 0a09s 002 r000 1 of 1
